  <recipe>
    <head>
      <title>Basil Mashed Potatoes 2</title>
      <categories>
        <cat>Ew</cat>
        <cat>Text</cat>
        <cat>Import</cat></categories>
      <yield>1</yield></head>
    <ingredients>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>4</qty>
          <unit/></amt>
        <item>Potatoes,; peeled</item></ing>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>3</qty>
          <unit>tablespoons</unit></amt>
        <item>Butter</item></ing>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty/>
          <unit/></amt>
        <item>Salt</item></ing>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>1/4</qty>
          <unit>cups</unit></amt>
        <item>Heavy cream</item></ing>
      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>1</qty>
          <unit>cup</unit></amt>
        <item>Pesto</item></ing></ingredients>
    <directions>
      <step>  Boil potatoes until tender. With masher, mash potatoes. Add butter and
  salt. Slowly add cream and stir until combined. Fold in 1 cup of pesto.
  Serve.
